==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tamarack
<hw>Tam"a*rack</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<sd>(a)</sd> <def>The American larch; also, the larch of Oregon and
British Columbia (<spn>Larix occidentalis</spn>). See
<er>Hackmatack</er>, and <er>Larch</er>.</def> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>The
black pine (<spn>Pinus Murrayana</spn>) of Alaska, California, etc. It
is a small tree with fine-grained wood.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tamaric</ent>⟦br⟧
